{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-reading-time","description":"Adds an estimated reading time field to all remark nodes","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","remark","reading time","node","medium","estimate"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"garetmckinley","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/15500c3c7e1fbedea2b087c7c8b337b5"},"repository":null,"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-reading-time\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-reading-time\" aria-label=\"gatsby remark reading time permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-reading-time</h1>\n<p>Adds a medium-like reading time estimate to your gatsby remark posts. Powered by <a href=\"https://github.com/ngryman/reading-time\"><code class=\"language-text\">reading-time</code></a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-label=\"installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Install</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yarn add gatsby-remark-reading-time</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Add to <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code> plugins in <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-reading-time`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>The reading time can be queried in the fields of markdownRemark nodes. An example of this in a single post would look like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> query <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> graphql<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n  query($slug: String!) {\n    markdownRemark(fields: { slug: { eq: $slug } }) {\n      htmlAst\n      excerpt(pruneLength: 200)\n      frontmatter {\n        title\n        date(formatString: \"MMMM Do, YYYY\")\n      }\n      fields {\n        slug\n        readingTime {\n          text\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>There are 4 available values in <code class=\"language-text\">readingTime</code>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">text</code>: ‘1 min read’,</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">minutes</code>: 1,</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">time</code>: 60000,</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">words</code>: 200</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"license\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>License</h2>\n<p>MIT</p>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-reading-time/","id":"0740d7e5-df7e-5dee-aa44-533f48712ef5","layout":"plugins"}}